---
title: 'When Does More Context Make an AI Worse?'
date: '2026-07-11'
description: 'Persistent memory solves forgetting, but it can also make an AI less able to recognize when the task has changed.'
tags: ['ai-agents', 'context-engineering', 'memory', 'architecture']
